{"tid":465951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙11爆買】速遞員不滿要提早返工 化身「小志強」狂踢包裹","createTime":"2017-11-12T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T06:00:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"900d396a3f128256ea47a837b662efced2956e9d","tid":465951,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171112/large/1510465591_0803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171112%2Flarge%2F1510465591_0803.jpg&h=bb6d1f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無數網民在雙11購物節瘋狂掃貨。網民簡單訂貨程序後，其餘要靠速遞員將貨件送到買家手上。惟昨日，江蘇鹽城亭湖區一韻達快遞服務部，兩名快遞員因不滿雙11提前上班，便竟在貨車上狂踢包裹。影片所見，速遞員視包裹如足球般，踢來踢去，臉露笑容。目前韻達快遞已報警，並表示會追究兩人法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171112/57448862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F57448862&d=m0e3U0I%2B%2Bcs63X%2BT%2FLg42v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2b9e7650\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F57448862&h=b71b8663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171112/57448862</a>"},{"pid":"41729239351649011a0f75e6ef469432bbf8b7fd","tid":465951,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港順x嗰啲成日都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0429bbcc0c03db6a48626ef53cec5486d105e8c4","tid":465951,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"順X速遞咪差唔多,將D包裹好似籃球咁掉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}